    {
        "content": "<p>Can you un-#xy your self and describe what <code>A</code> and <code>B</code> and <code>foo</code> are? There are multiple ways to deal with this: <code>outParam</code>s, type synonyms, explicit <code>letI</code>s, etc and it might not be easy to choose which to do.</p>",
