    {
        "content": "<p>In that case I would suggest</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CoxeterSystem</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Group</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CoxeterSystem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">W</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">W</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LT</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">cs</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Group</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">where</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">lt</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">lt</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">cs</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
